  <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
  <span>4 min read</span>
</div>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes, AG is a valid Scrabble word in both TWL and SOWPODS, scoring 3 points. Short for agriculture, AG is one of the most hook-friendly 2-letter words available — with 13 front-hooks (BAG, DAG, FAG, GAG, HAG, JAG, LAG, MAG, NAG, RAG, SAG, TAG, WAG) and useful back-hooks (AGE, AGO, AGS). It's a setup play that creates scoring lanes for yourself or traps for your opponent.</p>

