  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">AG is short for agriculture, accepted in all official Scrabble dictionaries. Like AD, it boasts 13 front-hooks — making it one of the two most extendable 2-letter words in the game. The G tile appears only 3 times in the bag, so using it efficiently matters.</p>
